<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="aff-page">

    <\!-- Hero -->
    <p class="aff-hero__eyebrow">Affiliate Program</p>
    <h1 class="aff-hero__h1">You teach the patterns.<br>HoldOff catches them at 11 PM.</h1>
    <p class="aff-hero__subhead">
      Partner with HoldOff and earn 30% recurring commission for every client or follower
      who subscribes through your referral link. No code required. No cap on earnings.
    </p>

    <\!-- How it works -->
    <div class="aff-section">
      <h2 class="aff-section__heading">How it works</h2>
      <div class="aff-steps">
        <div class="aff-step">
          <div class="aff-step__num">1</div>
          <p class="aff-step__text"><strong>Apply below.</strong> We review every application manually — we want partners who genuinely work with attachment patterns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="aff-step">
          <div class="aff-step__num">2</div>
          <p class="aff-step__text"><strong>Get your unique link.</strong> Your link looks like: <code style="font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--accent);">shouldiholdoff.live/?aff=yourcode</code>. Share it anywhere — social, newsletter, session handouts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="aff-step">
          <div class="aff-step__num">3</div>
          <p class="aff-step__text"><strong>90-day attribution cookie.</strong> Anyone who clicks your link has it attributed to you for 90 days. They can come back a month later and you still get credit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="aff-step">
          <div class="aff-step__num">4</div>
          <p class="aff-step__text"><strong>Get paid monthly.</strong> 30% of every subscription payment, for the life of the subscriber. No clawbacks on renewals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="aff-callout">
        <div class="aff-callout__stat">
          <div class="aff-callout__number">30%</div>
          <div class="aff-callout__label">recurring commission on every payment,<br>for the lifetime of the subscription</div>
        </div>
        <div class="aff-callout__stat">
          <div class="aff-callout__number">90</div>
          <div class="aff-callout__label">day attribution window — clicks from your link<br>are credited for 3 months</div>
        </div>
        <div class="aff-callout__stat">
          <div class="aff-callout__number">$0</div>
          <div class="aff-callout__label">cost to join — no fees, no minimums,<br>no exclusivity requirements</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <\!-- Why partner -->
    <div class="aff-section">
      <h2 class="aff-section__heading">Why partner with HoldOff</h2>
      <p class="aff-section__body">
        Your clients do the work in session. Then they go home, get a text at 11 PM that sets off every pattern you've been working on together — and there's nothing standing between them and the send button.
      </p>
      <p class="aff-section__body">HoldOff is that pause.</p>
      <ul class="aff-why-list">
        <li>It works between sessions, not instead of them. You stay the clinician.</li>
        <li>No intake forms, no credentials required — clients self-install in 2 minutes.</li>
        <li>The AI explains <em>why</em> it's flagging a message (protest behavior, reassurance bid, double text) using the same language you use in session.</li>
        <li>It intercepts the real thing on Android — not a journaling app. When the message is drafted, HoldOff catches it.</li>
        <li>Pricing starts at $19.99/month — less than one co-pay.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <\!-- Signup form -->
    <div class="aff-form" id="affSignupSection">
      <h2 class="aff-form__heading">Apply to partner</h2>
      <p class="aff-form__sub">Takes 60 seconds. We'll review and reply within a few business days.</p>
      <form id="affSignupForm">
        <div class="aff-form__fields">
          <div class="aff-form__field">
            <label class="aff-form__label" for="affName">Your name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="affName" name="name" class="aff-form__input" placeholder="Dr. Sarah Kim" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="aff-form__field">
            <label class="aff-form__label" for="affEmail">Email *</label>
            <input type="email" id="affEmail" name="email" class="aff-form__input" placeholder="sarah@yourpractice.com" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
          <div class="aff-form__field">
            <label class="aff-form__label" for="affPractice">Practice or handle</label>
            <input type="text" id="affPractice" name="practiceHandle" class="aff-form__input" placeholder="@sarahkimtherapy or yoursite.com" />
          </div>
          <div class="aff-form__field">
            <label class="aff-form__label" for="affAudience">Audience size</label>
            <select id="affAudience" name="audienceSize" class="aff-form__select">
              <option value="">Prefer not to say</option>
              <option value="0-500">0–500 (clients / followers)</option>
              <option value="500-2000">500–2,000</option>
              <option value="2000-10000">2,000–10,000</option>
              <option value="10000+">10,000+</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="aff-form__btn" id="affSubmitBtn">Apply now →</button>
      </form>
      <p class="aff-form__confirm" id="affConfirm" hidden>
        Application received. <em>Check your inbox for next steps.</em>
      </p>
      <p class="aff-form__note">By applying you confirm you'll disclose the affiliate relationship wherever required by your professional code or advertising regulations.</p>
    </div>

    <\!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="aff-faq">
      <h2 class="aff-faq__heading">Frequently asked questions</h2>

      <div class="aff-faq__item">
        <p class="aff-faq__q">How does the 30% commission work?</p>
        <p class="aff-faq__a">You earn 30% of every monthly or annual payment made by a subscriber you referred, for the lifetime of their subscription. If someone you referred stays subscribed for two years, you keep getting paid every month.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aff-faq__item">
        <p class="aff-faq__q">How long is the attribution window?</p>
        <p class="aff-faq__a">90 days. If someone clicks your referral link and subscribes anytime within 90 days of that click, the conversion is credited to you — even if they close the tab and come back later.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aff-faq__item">
        <p class="aff-faq__q">When do I get paid?</p>
        <p class="aff-faq__a">Payouts are processed monthly once you have at least $25 in earned commissions. V1 uses manual transfer (bank or PayPal). Stripe Connect automation is on the roadmap.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aff-faq__item">
        <p class="aff-faq__q">What happens if a subscriber cancels?</p>
        <p class="aff-faq__a">Commission stops when the subscription ends. If they re-subscribe later through your link within the 90-day window, attribution resets and you earn again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aff-faq__item">
        <p class="aff-faq__q">Is there a compliance issue recommending an app to my clients?</p>
        <p class="aff-faq__a">HoldOff is a self-help tool, not a clinical intervention — the same category as a book, a podcast, or a journal you might recommend. You disclose the affiliate relationship to clients wherever required by your professional code (NASW, APA, NBCC, etc.) and use your clinical judgment about fit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aff-faq__item">
        <p class="aff-faq__q">Can I apply as a content creator, not a therapist?</p>
        <p class="aff-faq__a">Yes. Coaches, podcasters, TikTok creators, and newsletter writers who address anxious attachment are welcome. The form asks for your handle or audience size — just fill in what applies to you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <\!-- HoldOff Analytics --><!-- Analytics removed -->

  <script>
  (function () {
    var form = document.getElementById('affSignupForm');
    var confirmEl = document.getElementById('affConfirm');
    var submitBtn = document.getElementById('affSubmitBtn');
    if (\!form) return;

    form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      var name = form.querySelector('[name="name"]').value.trim();
      var email = form.querySelector('[name="email"]').value.trim();
      var practiceHandle = form.querySelector('[name="practiceHandle"]').value.trim();
      var audienceSize = form.querySelector('[name="audienceSize"]').value;

      if (\!name || \!email) return;

      submitBtn.disabled = true;
      submitBtn.textContent = 'Sending…';

      fetch('/api/affiliates/signup', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ name: name, email: email, practiceHandle: practiceHandle, audienceSize: audienceSize })
      })
        .then(function (r) { return r.json(); })
        .then(function () {
          form.hidden = true;
          confirmEl.hidden = false;
          if (typeof fbq \!== 'undefined') fbq('track', 'Lead', { content_name: 'affiliate_signup' });
        })
        .catch(function () {
          submitBtn.disabled = false;
          submitBtn.textContent = 'Apply now →';
          alert('Something went wrong. Please try again.');
        });
    });
  })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
